{"tid":2272924,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大三罷港鐵沙田站遭破壞 三男女被控今提堂","createTime":"2020-11-05T11:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T12:03:47.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b415cbe848c7fb85c4e31a6b0c6f78a881403e3b","tid":2272924,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:16:24.000Z","msg":"去年11月11日網民發起「大三罷」，示威者在全港多區堵路及破壞港鐵設施，當日港鐵沙田站的閘機、閉路電視、以及客務中心玻璃與電腦均被破壞。警方事後拘控兩男一女，三人被控刑事損壞、非法集結及蒙面等罪，案件今首度提訊。裁判官應辯方要求，將案件押後至12月29日再訊，以待辯方索取文件。<br />\n<br />\n三人亦各被控一項在身處非法集結時使用蒙面物品罪，林被指使用頭套，龔則使用面罩，而梁則使用一件衫。<br />\n<br />\n辯方申請押後，以便向控方索取文件。裁判官照准，三人獲准各以3,000元保釋外出候訊。"},{"pid":"158bc571cc23eb7546e1774907fb5df6d0688fa8","tid":2272924,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:16:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/F3LT3IBZDFD3HILKAR5RBWEEKU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2FF3LT3IBZDFD3HILKAR5RBWEEKU%2F&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4M3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=19acd14a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201105%2FF3LT3IBZDFD3HILKAR5RBWEEKU%2F&h=feea05b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201105/F3LT3IBZDFD3HILKAR5RBWEEKU/</a>"},{"pid":"6b23c502535d7b913a12114f0cbfdb3869d142af","tid":2272924,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}